skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: graded card look up
des:
Say the certification number for a PSA graded trading card and Alexa gives you the current population for that card, for that grade.

"PSA Graded Card Look Up" has an in-skill purchase option available! You can get the following additional information added to your response for the certification numbers you submit:

- Label Type
- Reverse Cert Number/Barcode
- Year
- Brand
- Sport
- Card Number
- Player
- Variety/Pedigree
- Card Grade
- PSA/DNA Certified
- Autograph Grade
- Primary Signer
- SMR Price Guide Value
- Population Higher

Anything that would be displayed on the PSA certification verification page is included.
